      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like im living in a vacuum sometimes. i work from this apartment, i talk to people on screens, i go to the grocery store... but i dont think anyone actually sees me. like i could just stop existing and the world would just keep spinning without a single hiccup. does that make sense?",
